Can I have separate accounts for different locations?

I have multiple coffee shops with different managers who place orders. How will that work? Easy! We can set up one account for your coffee shop group but each manager can have their own log in crendentias and will be able to place orders for their location.

When will my delivery arrive?

Most of our products with arrive next day. Delivery windows are clearly indicated at check out so you always know when to expect your delivery.

Can I request products from specific suppliers that aren't on the list?

Of course! This is a living breathing store that we're building for YOU, and updates will happen often. Don't see an item you wish to purchase from a certain supplier? No problem, we'll reach out to our guys with you in mind.

How will I be charged?

CUPS will charge your credit card according to your payment terms. By default, each shop starts with 1 day terms, but if you'd like to extend this period, contact us.
